\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ποτε\">ΠΟΤΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τοῦτον\">ΤΟΥΤΟΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀνεῖ\n                    λε\">[.]ΝΕΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΛΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"κίων\">ΚΙΩΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"καὶ\">ΚΑΙ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Μοῖρα\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μοῖρα\">ΜΟΙΡΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ὃς\">ΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"κατέλειψε\">ΚΑΤΕΛΕΙΨΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"πατρὶ\">ΠΑΤΡΙ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"λύπην\">ΛΥΠΗΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"δεινοτάτην\">ΔΕΙΝΟΤΑΤΗΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al8-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησε\">ΕΖΗΣΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>.Β\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002750_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic002750_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic002750.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-05-09\" src=\"ISic002750-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Manganaro 1994 but controlled with